    "Workspace member listing is ~30% faster for workspaces with 50–200 members, addressing slow load times flagged by high-volume customers.",
    "API quickstart updated to clearly explain the current auth model, reducing integration friction for developers new to the platform.",
    "First-run dashboard now surfaces inline tooltips for active users, retention, billing, and integrations — the four metrics new users most commonly miss."
  ],
  "customer_voice": "Enterprise customers ranked dashboard sluggishness as their top complaint in the Q2 NPS survey, and product analytics showed a steady stream of signups abandoned at step 3 of the old five-step flow; this release attacks both pain points head-on while also smoothing the integration experience for developers who found the auth docs confusing."
}

